<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="pt-BR">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Pagamento Confirmado - StudyWob</title>
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.1.3/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        .success-container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 50px auto;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 30px;
        }
        .success-icon {
            color: #28a745;
            font-size: 64px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        .company-details {
            background: #f8f9fa;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            margin-top: 30px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="success-container">
            <div class="success-icon">
                ✓
            </div>
            <h1 class="mb-4">Pagamento Confirmado!</h1>
            <p class="lead">
                Parabéns! Sua assinatura foi ativada com sucesso.
            </p>

            <div class="company-details">
                <h3>Detalhes da Empresa</h3>
                <p><strong>Nome:</strong> <%= company.name %></p>
                <p><strong>Email:</strong> <%= company.email %></p>
                <p><strong>Domínio:</strong> <%= company.domain %></p>
                <p><strong>Plano:</strong> <%= company.plan.charAt(0).toUpperCase() + company.plan.slice(1) %></p>
            </div>

            <div class="mt-4">
                <p>
                    Enviamos um email com as instruções de acesso para
                    <strong><%= company.email %></strong>
                </p>
                <p class="small text-muted">
                    Se não encontrar o email, verifique sua caixa de spam.
                </p>
            </div>

            <div class="mt-5">
                <a href="/" class="btn btn-primary">Voltar para Home</a>
                <a href="/login" class="btn btn-outline-primary ms-2">Fazer Login</a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.1.3/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"></script>
</body>
</html> 